# AsyncImagePhase.empty

**Case**

No image is loaded.

## Declaration

```swift
case empty
```

## Getting load phases

- **AsyncImagePhase.success(_:)**: An image successfully loaded.
- **AsyncImagePhase.failure(_:)**: An image failed to load with an error.
